title: Lil Baby Is No. 1, but Taylor Swift’s Huge Chart Takeover Nears
description: The singer-songwriter’s new album, “Midnights,” won’t hit the Billboard 200 until next week, but after just one weekend it is already the year’s biggest-selling LP.
dc:creator: Ben Sisario
media:description: Lil Baby’s “It’s Only Me” is his third No. 1 album in three years.
